# Intricare Task — Complete Implementation Plan

> This document is the single source of truth for converting the Figma design into high-fidelity Vue + Vuetify pages inside the **starter-kit** project. Any developer (or AI agent in a new chat) can pick this up and execute without breaking the flow.

---

## 1. Project Overview

**Goal:** Convert the provided Figma design (`Intricare Task`) into pixel-accurate, fully responsive web pages using the Vuetify-based `starter-kit` under:

```
c:\Users\hp\Downloads\vuetify\vue-laravel-version\typescript-version\starter-kit\
```

**Tech Stack:**
- Vue 3 (Composition API + `<script setup lang="ts">`)
- Vuetify 3 (wired via `resources/ts/plugins/vuetify/`)
- TypeScript
- SCSS (via `resources/styles/`)
- Vite + Laravel Vite plugin
- unplugin-vue-router (file-based routing from `resources/ts/pages/`)

---

## 2. Figma Design — Screen Inventory

**Figma File:** https://www.figma.com/design/G6loxh8mLuApHQgT5BZjuH/Intricare-Task

The canvas is organised into **two section groups**:

### Group A — Standard Workflow (4 screens)

| # | Frame Name | Description |
|---|-----------|-------------|
| 1 | **Standard** | Modal popup: "Select Workflow Mode" — choose Advanced or Standard |
| 2 | **Leads List** | Sidebar + main area: Campaign breadcrumb, step progress indicator |
| 3 | **Target Audience** | 3 import method cards + LinkedIn URL input area |
| 4 | **Sequence** | 3-step bar (Leads List → Target Audience → Campaign); linear sequence builder |

### Group B — Advanced Workflow (10+ screens)

| # | Node ID | Description |
|---|---------|-------------|
| 1 | 1-1637 | LinkedIn Search selected: 4 cards + "Paste LinkedIn Search URL" section with Validate |
| 2 | 1-2041 | Upload CSV File selected: 4 cards + drag-and-drop upload area |
| 3 | 1-2136 | CSV uploaded state: green checkmarks on Steps 1 & 2 + Map Properties begins |
| 4 | 1-2221 | Map Properties full view: 3-column table (Contact Field | CSV Column | Unmapped) |
| 5+ | various | Sender Profiles tab, dark mode states, user profile dropdown popup |

