## 3. Color Palette

All colors defined in two places:
1. CSS vars in `resources/styles/variables/_template.scss`
2. Vuetify theme tokens in `resources/ts/plugins/vuetify/theme.ts`

| Variable | Hex | Usage |
|----------|-----|-------|
| `--fig-white` | `#FFFFFF` | Backgrounds, cards |
| `--fig-bg-light` | `#F8F8F8` | Page background |
| `--fig-bg-blue-tint` | `#F6F8FF` | Selected card bg, content area |
| `--fig-success` | `#28C76F` | Step complete dots, badges |
| `--fig-primary-light` | `#CFDAFE` | Active nav bg, step lines |
| `--fig-border` | `#B1B1B1` | Borders, dividers |
| `--fig-text-dark` | `#5E5873` | Body text, labels |
| `--fig-text-muted` | `#9692A4` | Placeholder, muted text |
| `--fig-primary` | `#3666EE` | Primary blue: buttons, links, active |
| `--fig-bg-page` | `#F9FBFF` | Outermost page background |
| `--fig-bg-subtle` | `#F6F6F6` | Table header row |
| **Btn Gradient** | `#8BA6FF → #3762EE` | All primary action buttons |

### Vuetify theme.ts updates (light theme):
```ts
'primary': '#3666EE',
'primary-darken-1': '#3762EE',
'success': '#28C76F',
'background': '#F9FBFF',
'surface': '#FFFFFF',
'on-surface': '#5E5873',
```

