## 4. Typography

- **Font family:** Keep existing, ensure `Inter` loaded in `webfontloader.ts`
- **Nav label:** 14px, weight 500, `#5E5873`
- **Breadcrumb:** 13px; active=`#3666EE`, inactive=`#5E5873`
- **Step badge:** 11px, weight 600
- **Card title:** 14px, weight 600, `#5E5873`
- **Card subtitle:** 12px, weight 400, `#9692A4`
- **Section headings:** use Vuetify `text-h5` / `text-h6`

---

## 5. Layout & Spacing

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Sidebar width | 260px (full) / 68px (collapsed) |
| Content padding | `24px` all sides |
| Card inner padding | `16px` |
| Section gap | `24px` |
| Border radius – cards | `8px` |
| Border radius – buttons | `6px` |
| Border radius – inputs | `4px` |

**Responsive breakpoints:**

| Breakpoint | Behaviour |
|-----------|-----------|
| `xs` < 600px | Sidebar = drawer, cards stack 1-col, modal full-screen |
| `sm` 600–960px | Sidebar = overlay drawer, 2-col import cards |
| `md` 960–1280px | Sidebar = overlay, 2-col import cards |
| `lg+` ≥ 1280px | Full sidebar 260px, 4-col import cards |

