## 9. Reusable Components — Props/Emits

### `AppStepProgress.vue`
```ts
defineProps<{
  steps: Array<{ label: string; icon: string }>
  current: number  // 1-based
}>()
```
Renders horizontal bar with connecting lines. Done=green ✓, Active=blue filled, Pending=grey outline.

### `SelectWorkflowModal.vue`
```ts
defineProps<{ modelValue: boolean }>()
defineEmits<{ 'update:modelValue': [val: boolean]; selected: [type: 'advanced' | 'standard'] }>()
```

### `ImportMethodSelector.vue`
```ts
defineProps<{ modelValue: 'linkedin' | 'csv' | 'lookalike' | 'webhook' }>()
defineEmits<{ 'update:modelValue': [val: string] }>()
```

### `CsvUploadArea.vue`
```ts
defineEmits<{ 'file-uploaded': [file: File] }>()
```
Drag-and-drop with `@dragover`, `@drop` events. Also has `<input type="file">` browse trigger.

### `MapPropertiesTable.vue`
```ts
defineProps<{
  csvColumns: string[]
  contactFields: Array<{ label: string; key: string }>
}>()
defineEmits<{ mapped: [mapping: Record<string, string>] }>()
```

### `SequenceBuilder.vue`
Internal state only. Steps array with add/remove/reorder. Each step has: type, message, wait config.

